    "description": "FEA predicts construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw design under ASTM F1717 static compression-bending. Validated by direct comparison to bench testing (N=11 constructs across two laboratories). Model influence MEDIUM (testing confirms results); decision consequence MEDIUM (pedicle screw fracture leads to revision surgery, not death).",
