      "name": "Compression-bending QoI comparison: FEA vs. N=11 constructs",
      "description": "FEA-predicted stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are compared against N=11 physical constructs tested across two independent laboratories. All three QoIs fall within the pre-specified 10% acceptance band; the normalized validation metric E/uval remains below 1.96 for all QoIs, satisfying the acceptance criterion. The observational study design captured naturally occurring variability in implant lot and operator technique, providing a rich empirical basis for the comparison.",
      "validationMetric": "E/uval",
