        "type": "Activity",
        "activityType": "observational-study",
        "name": "ASTM F1717 compression-bending data collection — observational cohort",
        "description": "Bench-test records from eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs were prospectively collected across two contract testing laboratories operating under their standard ASTM F1717 protocols. Specimen selection, fixture setup, and load-application rate followed each laboratory's established procedures without additional experimental controls imposed by the modeling team. Load-displacement curves, stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement were extracted and transferred to the FEA team for QoI comparison. The breadth of the dataset — spanning two independent facilities, two implant manufacturing lots, and three operators — substantially strengthens confidence in the generalizability of the validation findings.",
        "startedAtTime": "2024-06-01T00:00:00Z",
